Text: Yes, how does the keygen works. The generator says that I shall write my serial code but when I tried to write it I only can write the numbers, not with words. I have a serial with only numbers but the generator only say it's wrong serial. How shall I do? Hope someone can help me. Thanks.
Im looking for the final ut pro pluging for mac! anyone?

Hi i have had to register so i can tel you how to use the keygen properly
1st you need to open the keygen oviusly
2nd open the plugin in your DAW and click on tools
3rd click unlock and you will see a box to put your code in just above it is a number copy and paste it into the 1st box on the keygen the click generate and copy the code from the second box and paste it in the unlock box on the plugin and then you should get a message saying registration complete
Now you can enjoy the hole suit for free
Enjoy!!! hope this helped
